title: STUNNING UNIT IN ONE PARAISO!!
posting_body: ['Stunning 2-bed/2-bath unit with private elevator and foyer.', 'Finished with top-of-the-line white calacatta marble flooring throughout (the balcony included).', 'Electrical shades and blackouts.', 'Imported Italian closets in both bedrooms.', 'Not a dime saved on lighting fixtures.', 'The ocean view of the unit is breathtaking and unobstructed from its enormous balcony.', 'The Paraiso complex offers a 3-acre resort deck with a heated swimming pool, outdoor spa, poolside cabanas, summer kitchen, jogging circuit and beautifully landscaped sun terrace.', 'Residents enjoy a clubroom with billiards, fitness center, health spa with steam and sauna facilities, private screening room, wine cellar, cigar lounge, and a bayfront beach club and marina', 'all units are one year lease min!', 'credit score close to 700 or higher required, proof of income 2,5 greater than rent price, first month + last month + security deposit to move in!', 'Dilya Taveras', 'Equity Realty', 'TEXT :', 'show contact info']
